      "content": "it's not just a \"tough time\" though. it's like the soul has been ripped out of everything. even the sun feels cold. i look at my life and there's just no point in performing these little daily rituals when the person who made it all mean something is just... gone. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting an empty house.",
